      "span_text": "The group W acts on the Bass-Serre tree T corresponding to the amalgamated product W ¼ X Ã Y Z and therefore U stabilizes a vertex of T. But the only vertex stabilized by b is the vertex v with Stab v ¼ X because b is not conjugate in X to an element of Y; it follows that o fixes v, i.e. that o is an element of X. This completes [CITATION_1] .",
